        "path": "cronos-the-new-dawn-trainer/requirements.txt",
        "content": "# Cronos: The New Dawn Trainer - Dependencies\n# This is a C# project using .NET, so no external packages are required.\n# The project targets .NET 6.0 or later.\n#\n# To build and run:\n# 1. Install .NET SDK 6.0+ from https://dotnet.microsoft.com/download\n# 2. Navigate to project directory\n# 3. Run: dotnet build\n# 4. Run: dotnet run\n#\n# Note: The trainer uses P/Invoke to kernel32.dll for memory operations.\n# It must be run with administrator privileges to attach to the game process.\n"
